'''市场观察'''（{{lang-en|MarketWatch}}<ref name="陈琳琳">{{cite book|author=陈琳琳|title=《中国经济底气》|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Hj64DQAAQBAJ&pg=PT132|publisher=财大出版社|isbn=978-1-68182-085-9|pages=132–}}</ref>）是一个提供[[金融|金融]][[信息|信息]]、商业新闻、[[分析|分析]]和[[股市|股市]]数据的网站，总部位于[[美国|美国]][[纽约市|纽约]]<ref name="Carbasho2010">{{cite book|author=Tracy Carbasho|title=Nike|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pCT05HUsYZ8C&pg=PA48|date=19 August 2010|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-1-59884-343-9|pages=48–|access-date=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716101025/https://books.google.com/books?id=pCT05HUsYZ8C&pg=PA48|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》和《[[巴伦周刊|巴伦周刊]]》一样，它是[[新闻集团|新闻集团]]的子公司[[道琼斯公司|道琼斯公司]]的全资子公司<ref name="Plunkett2007">{{cite book|author=Jack W. Plunkett|title=Plunkett's E-Commerce & Internet Business Almanac 2007|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RtjxG1W1JjAC&pg=PT411|date=February 2007|publisher=Plunkett Research, Ltd.|isbn=978-1-59392-065-4|pages=411–|access-date=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716103829/https://books.google.com/books?id=RtjxG1W1JjAC&pg=PT411|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
==历史沿革==
Marketwatch.com域名注册于1997年7月30日<ref>{{cite web | url=http://whois.domaintools.com/marketwatch.com | title=Whois Record for MarketWatch.com | work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]] | accessdate=2020-07-07 | archive-date=2021-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124152946/https://whois.domaintools.com/marketwatch.com | dead-url=no }}</ref>，1997年10月30日正式推出，[[汤姆·卡兰德拉|汤姆·卡兰德拉]]（Thom Calandra）担任网站主编<ref name=resigns>{{Cite news | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/4031390/ns/business-us_business/t/marketwatch-commentator-resigns-amid-probe/ | title=MarketWatch commentator resigns amid probe|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date=January 23, 2004}}</ref>。

2003年，[[大卫·卡拉威|大卫·卡拉威]]（David Callaway）接替卡兰德拉职务成为主编<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB1047049040128231680|title=MarketWatch Names New Editor|publisher=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|date=March 7, 2003|accessdate=2020-07-07|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122074232/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB1047049040128231680|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年1月，在[[互联网泡沫|互联网泡沫]]时期，Marketwatch实现[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]，每股定价17美元，募集资金4575万美元<ref>Dawn Kawamoto.{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/marketwatch-com-ipo-stuns-the-street/|title=Marketwatch.com IPO stuns the Street|date=Jan 2, 2002|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|access-date=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707124221/https://www.cnet.com/news/marketwatch-com-ipo-stuns-the-street/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2000年6月，与《[[金融时报|金融时报]]》成立合资企业，[[彼得·贝尔|彼得·贝尔]]（Peter Bale）担任总编辑<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.pearson.com/news-and-research/announcements/2000/03/ft-marketwatch-appoints-managing-editor.html | title=FT Marketwatch Appoints Managing Editor | publisher=Pearson | date=March 20, 2000 | accessdate=2020-07-07 | archive-date=2020-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025225209/https://www.pearson.com/news-and-research/announcements/2000/03/ft-marketwatch-appoints-managing-editor.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年1月，卡兰德拉辞职。2005年1月，道琼斯公司以5.28亿美元的总代价收购了MarketWatch<ref>{{cite news| url=https://techcrunch.com/2007/03/26/marketwatch-geting-all-web-2/| title=MarketWatch Adds Community Stock Predictor| publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]| date=Mar 26, 2007| accessdate=2020-07-07| archive-date=2020-08-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821080243/https://techcrunch.com/2007/03/26/marketwatch-geting-all-web-2/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

